Battera::

"heurg," was the sound she made as he grabbed her unexpectedly. She 
felt like yelling at him for not telling her that he was going to do 
that, but then, he was only trying to protect her and decided to keep 
her mouth shut.

--- In nbwrpg@egroups.com, "dachande" <Dachande85@m...> wrote:
> ::Dachande::
> 
>     "Who is this?" He said, still staring at Ares, but talking to 
Destructor. "And why do you think you can order me around.?"
>     Then he started talking to Battera. "I've challenged him to a 
duel, I cannot back down until the fight is done, nor can I allow 
anyone else in to the fight."
>     Suddenly he transformed to Beast Mode, but not under his own 
power. He whipped his tail at Ares, and then grabbed Battera and ran 
off, but towards the Destron Base.
